@DubyasNFT No kidding! That was such a good race. Those last 2 laps were crazy...

It was fun watching Kyle Busch evade just about EVERYTHING

And for number 14 to block at the end of stage 2 for lead lap and then get third... What a race, I'm a revamped fan, definitely watching the rest

@0xKNNY It's been that way for a while - coin to coins swaps are taxed based on the USD value at the time of swap, and same goes for NFTs

I'm not a tax expert but crypto kinda forces our hand to know the rules

A good practice is setting aside 40% of profits in USD of every sale/swap
